name: Lost in My Own Metaverse
description:
In these few days I didn't realize that I was immersed in the story of a chicken until I forgot who I really i am. I created him as an avatar in my own universe in my imagination. And also invites people to read and enjoy, and observe until they joined in my story. Now, I've created 37 imaginary realms and I call it my own metaverse. it's multidimensional and each dimension is related each others. I named it Indukayam Multi metaverse. Like a common chickens, he can't go far, if he gets lost he will be confused to find his way home
hmmm...Ok, nevermind ha ha ha...
